<h2>About Bug Tracker</h2>

<p>Bug Tracker is an application to track errors in software. It was built using ASP.NET MVC and C# with a Bootstrap template applied. It was created by Annette Arrigucci as part of the Coder Foundry summer 2016 class.</p>
<p><b>Roles:</b> A user can be assigned the roles of Admin, Project Manager, Developer and Submitter. A user can be in more than one role. Users are automatically placed in a Submitter role upon registration.</p>
<p><b>Ticket priorities:</b> A ticket can be Critical, High, Medium or Low priority.</p>
<p><b>Ticket statuses:</b> A ticket can be in New, Waiting for support, Waiting for customer, On hold or Resolved status.</p>
<p><b>Ticket types:</b> A ticket can be of type Error report, Service request, Feature request or Other.</p>

